.SH NAME
kc-list - List all keys in a vault


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBkc list [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Lists all key names stored in the active vault (or --vault). Values are not shown.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for list


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--vault\fP=""
	target vault (overrides active vault)


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBkc(1)\fP
